OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FShops tell people to buy in
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fstore instead of online    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, People should go into stores rather    
OL,6, than rely on online shopping if they   
OL,7, want to get Christmas gifts on time,   
OL,8, retailers have said, as postal strikes 
OL,9, delay parcel deliveries.               
OL,11,F"That's the advice we're giving," the  
OL,12,Fboss of bookseller Waterstones said.   
OL,14,FShopping in store will ensure          
OL,15,F"certainty", the British Independent   
OL,16,FRetailers Association (Bira) said.     
OL,18,FIt comes as Royal Mail staff continue  
OL,19,Fstrike action, in a row over pay and   
OL,20,Fconditions.                            
